OL,9,GHello! With only days remaining until
OL,10,Gwe open our stages the EMF team is
OL,11,Gfrantically laying cables, testing
OL,12,Glasers, and hanging bunting in
OL,13,Gpreparation for your arrival. This is
OL,14,Gprobably the last time you’ll hear
OL,15,Gfrom us before we open - but there’s a
OL,16,Gfew more things to tell you about. So
OL,17,Gmany volunteers After an overwhelming
OL,18,Gresponse to volunteer sign-up most
OL,19,Gslots are already full, but don’t
OL,20,Gworry, we expect to open up more
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
